{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2268643, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 436788, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "第一个用完之后要 close，第二个不用", "timestamp": 1628835752, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2268658, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 436788, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "或者换句话说，第一个的fp的生命周期会在close之前，第二个的fp的生命周期只存在于with里面", "timestamp": 1628835845, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2268665, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 436788, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "好像越解释越糊涂了hhh，Alice说的就没问题！", "timestamp": 1628835869, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2268670, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 436788, "reply_to": 2268665, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: Carol觉得Bob说的很清楚", "timestamp": 1628835906, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2268677, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 436788, "reply_to": 2268658, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 不是的，后面也可以用 fp，只是已经 close 了", "timestamp": 1628835931, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2268690, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 436788, "reply_to": 2268670, "tag": null, "text": "with 本质上只是出 with 的时候调用了 fp.__exit__()（进去的时候调用了 __enter__()），file stream 的 __exit__ 就是 close 掉，所以本质上就是节省了 close 操作", "timestamp": 1628836002, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2268692, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 436788, "reply_to": 2268670, "tag": null, "text": "双下划线被识别成了加粗，理解一下", "timestamp": 1628836021, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2268697, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 436788, "reply_to": 2268677, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 可以理解成可控制文件的范围是close前，作为变量的话生命周期应该是所在函数？", "timestamp": 1628836049, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2268707, "deleted": false, "i